data.description: WELCOME HOME!! Would you like a home with a TRUE mother-in-law suite?! Well, here it is!! This beautiful two story brick home in the sought-out Breezy Hill subdivision has a mother-in-law suite that has its very own full kitchen, laundry area, living room, bathroom & bedroom with a walk-in closet! This home will give you the space you need while still giving you a cozy feel. In the master bathroom you will find a double shower, large garden tub & two separate his and her vanities! This home provides a perfect split floorplan with 5 bedrooms downstairs & 1 bedroom upstairs along with the perfect game room or 2nd living area! Let's not forget the back patio that has the perfect fireplace to keep you warm on a winter night. As you look out while standing on the back patio, you will have a great view of the Koi fish pond (can stay or can be taken out), oversized backyard, along with a willow tree, peach tree, and more! Schedule your showing now!!
